**Hamravash Tips**

**How do I create a new app?**
If you are not familiar with the Hamravash platform, first watch this video. Also, the Hamravash docs explain the process of creating an app well.

**What can I do to prevent my Hamravash credits from running out quickly?**
When creating a new app, always be sure to set the resources to the minimum possible. Later, by checking the "Resource Consumption" tab for the desired app in Darkube, if you observe that the service resources are low, you can increase the system's resources from the "Resource Management" section.

**What can I do to prevent others from sending requests to my service?**
For this purpose, you can select the "Enable Authentication" option for your service in the "Domain Address" section and then register the address containing a user/pass in the competition panel.
For example:
`https://user:pass@your-app-name.darkube.app`

**What should I do if my Hamravash credit runs out?**
Based on our assessment, the gifted credit is sufficient for the 10-day duration of the competition. However, if your credit runs out, you can submit your request by contacting the competition support via Telegram at @torobTurbo.

