**Architecture Tips**

**What should the service architecture be like?**
In general, try to first implement the simplest thing that comes to your mind (zero scenario), and then gradually make your assistant smarter. As one of the initial tasks, be sure to save the logs of requests made to you somewhere. And check what requests are being sent to your service. Then, based on these requests, you should develop different tools for your assistant to help it generate better answers.